Now, Im gonna admit that this is a bit unfair and unscientific, but I think it also reinforces the fact that 1Handers with Dual Wield are still better damage compared to 2Handers.<BR> <A HREF="http://pub2.ezboard.com/fthesafehousethebackroomsecretsspoilers.showMessage?topicID=1671.topic" TARGET=_blank>http://pub2.ezboard.com/fthesafehousethebackroomsecretsspoilers.showMessage?topicID=1671.topic</A> <P>Of course, the rogue in question doesnt mention who ended up tanking the whole time, or that the warrior/SK group probably didnt have a bard, or anything.  Not trying to say that Rogues are superior to anyone, just that 2handed weapons are not the optimal choice for warriors in most circumstances.  <IMG SRC="http://www.baelish.aust.com/tritonforum/smile.gif"><P>That being said, another big congrats to Dread for getting Soul Leech!  It might not be Dual Wield, but its the next best thing, and he's gonna kick major ass now!<P>Jalowan
